<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
      .header { background: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
      .button { background: #007bff; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0; }
      .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #6c757d; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Application Update</h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello <%= @user.first_name %>,</h2>
        
        <p>Thank you for your interest in <%= @app_name %>.</p>
        
        <p>After careful review, we're unable to approve your trader account application at this time.</p>
        
        <p>This decision may be due to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Incomplete information provided</li>
          <li>Documentation requirements not met</li>
          <li>Current capacity limitations</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>You're welcome to reapply in the future or contact our support team for more information.</p>
        
        <a href="mailto:support@stocktrader.com" class="button">Contact Support</a>
        
        <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© 2025 <%= @app_name %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>